ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: This class is a fine introduction to ID and FMM methods as applied in real life. I would recommend this course if you are interested in a clear succinct presentation of sophisticated numerical methods to real life problems.
I would strongly recommend this class to anyone in applied mathematics.
